### Colour contrast
Contrast between foreground and background colours are tested to ensure [WCAG AA compliance](https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG20/#visual-audio-contrast-contrast). Where colour is used to draw attention to an item (e.g. [panel](/components/panel)) and insufficient contrast exists between a background colour and element colour, additional techniques may be required to provide support for users unable to perceive the colour.